title: MsgSettingsReadResp
description: The setting message with which the device responds after a MSG_SETTING_READ_REQ is sent to device. The string field is a NULL-terminated and NULL-delimited string with contents "SECTION_SETTING\0SETTING\0VALUE\0" where the '\0' escape sequence denotes the NULL character and where quotation marks are omitted. An example string that could be sent from device is "solution\0soln_freq\010\0".
